### Blocker:

**Git push requires authentication.** The system cannot authenticate to GitHub automatically. This is documented in `inbox/QUESTIONS.md`.

You need to manually set up git authentication using one of these methods:

1. **GitHub CLI** (recommended):
   ```bash
   gh auth login
   git push -u origin master
   ```

2. **Git credential helper**:
   ```bash
   git config credential.helper store
   git push -u origin master
   ```

3. **SSH**:
   ```bash
   git remote set-url origin git@github.com:cletcher/chaprola-fitlog.git
   git push -u origin master
   ```

Once you authenticate and push, all 15 commits (including the latest build logs) will be synced to GitHub.
